Harmony Gold Halts All Operations at Its Tshepong Mine After Worker Killed

-- B y   M k h u l u l i   M a n c o t y w a
-- 
2011-07-12T10:22:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/harmony-gold-halts-all-operations-at-its-tshepong-mine-after-worker-killed.html
Harmony Gold Mining Co. said “all
operations” have been stopped at its Tshepong mine in  South
Africa  after the death of a worker in an accident yesterday.  Harmony spokeswoman Henrika Basterfield commented by phone
from Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
